.TH "libnvme" 9 "struct libnbft_hfi" "April 2026" "API Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
struct libnbft_hfi \- Host Fabric Interface (HFI) Descriptor
.SH SYNOPSIS
struct libnbft_hfi {
.br
.BI "    int index;"
.br
.BI "    char transport[8];"
.br
.BI "    struct libnbft_hfi_info_tcp tcp_info;"
.br
.BI "
};
.br

.SH Members
.IP "index" 12
HFI Descriptor Index: indicates the number of this HFI Descriptor
in the Host Fabric Interface Descriptor List.
.IP "transport" 12
Transport Type string (e.g. 'tcp').
.IP "tcp_info" 12
The HFI Transport Info Descriptor, see \fIstruct libnbft_hfi_info_tcp\fP.
